item.title: CVE-2023-0169|2024-08-02T05:02:44.043Z -- unknown -- form%20plugin%20for%20wordpress
item.description: The Zoho Forms WordPress plugin before 3.0.1 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
